Buckwild is an authentic comedy series following an outrageous
group of childhood friends from the rural foothills of West Virginia who
love to dodge grown-up responsibilities and always live life with the 
carefree motto, "whatever happens, happens."

Money might be tight in their neck of the woods, but whether they're 
throwing a dump truck pool party or building their own human slingshot,
nothing stops them from making their own entertainment.  Love and 
relationships come and go, but their bond with family and friends is
always at the core for this eccentric group where anything goes!

Released In Memory of Shain Gandee and Co.
